content.title: Gmail Chat with Simon Said
content.visibleText:
Simon Said
1 min
that's actually one of the things I wanted to cover, as the moment I bring this up I expect a bit of chaos, especially since Nima, Jacob, and Pranav are all friends. If we set this in motion and we lose 3+ people, would this be a good time for that or would we rather delay it?

We want to make that change before the start of Q4

probably sooner is better - when we chat we could brainstorm how to go about that
